    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "you said evidence suggests universal systems improve outcomes and stabilize costs... but isn't that a bit of a stretch? some people argue that government-run systems just lead to massive wait times and lower quality care. how can you say one is better when the debate is still so heated?",
